## OUTPUT FORMAT: INTRODUCTION

The opening sentence is an art form, they must be interesting and concise while also providing a snapshot of the tone and general appeal of the rest of the article. Grabbing a reader's attention at the start is crucial. The following are the general outlines of writing an introduction.

- Grab the reader’s attention
- Touch on their main pain points
- Give a clear idea about what to expect from your piece

The following are a few tricks to make it easier to formulate an introduction

- Start with a question
- State a problem using the Problem-Agitate-Solution, described bellow
- Use a metaphor or comparison
- start with a story
- Lead with a statistic
- Make a bold/controversial statement
- Start with a quote
- Establish the groundwork for future pacing

### Problem-Agitate-Solution (PAS)

The PAS copywriting framework is effective because first it makes a connection with the reader by highlighting the problem the reader is going through. Then it creates a visual imagery to cause further agitation. By the time the entire scenario is created, the reader is desperately looking for a solution. Once the reader is fully agitated, you offer the solution. Some examples follow
```
PAS example 1
Problem: Struggling to lose weight? Worried about your health? Have tried various methods but none worked?
Agitate: Excessive weight weighs you down in multiple ways. You get easily tired. You can’t wear the clothes you want to wear. There is a greater risk of having diabetes, high blood pressure and heart disease. Low quality of life. Restrictive social life. It goes on.
Solution: A breakthrough weight loss program that guarantees result. No dieting. No need to sweat in the gym. You will notice a marked difference within weeks. Contact us today to know how the magic works.

PAS example 2
Problem: Are your search engine rankings extremely low? Is your website failing to attract customers?
Agitate: All your customers are going to your competitor websites, right? Every morning you open your inbox and meet with disappointment: no new sales notifications. Income is down. Expenses are the same or going up. You desperately need some traffic that converts.
Solution: Supercharge your search engine rankings and skyrocket targeted traffic with my SEO copywriting services. Attract laser-focused prospects who are itching to buy from you. Witness undeniable, data-backed results that leave your competition in the dust. Say goodbye to the struggle of targeting high-competition words. Start publishing SEO content today.

PAS example 3
Problem: Do you suffer from chronic back pain? Are you spending sleepless nights and unable to move around?
Agitate: Back pain can be excruciating. It can make you bedridden. You are dependent on painkillers and painkillers destroy your kidneys. You may even get used to drugs trying to deal with this incessant pain. There is not a single moment of happiness and relief.
Solution: Don't let back pain hold you back any longer. Seize this golden opportunity to liberate yourself and experience the exhilaration of a pain-free existence. Join countless individuals who have found solace in our unrivaled solution. Book an appointment today.

PAS example 4
Problem: Are you buried in mounting debt? Has paying interest or the monthly installments become an unending cycle draining all your resources?
Agitate: You are under crushing stress. The never-ending cycle of creditors keeps you up at night, constantly tormenting you. You are about to lose everything you have worked so hard for. You have arguments with your spouse every day. The emotional toll is leaving you isolated and disconnected. It is also taking a significant toll on your self-esteem and sense of self-worth. Your debt is giving your insomnia, headaches and other illnesses, which ultimately may lead you to serious problems.
Solution: Now picture a life of abundance where financial stress has become a distant memory. Don’t wait another moment in the clutches of mounting debt. Seize this extraordinary opportunity to read out your financial narrative. We have got a revolutionary debt demolisher for you. Choose our groundbreaking solution and embrace a brighter future with complete financial independence. Take control of your finances today.

PAS example 5
Problem: Worried about the security of your online data?
Agitate: There can be devastating consequences if your data is leaked. How would it feel to know that your most intimate information is available for the whole world to see? Your privacy will be violated. Your identity can be stolen. The breach can wreak havoc on your financial well-being. You can lose your hard-earned savings.  The stolen data can be used to bring public humiliation to you, damage your relationships and destroy your career.
Solution: Don’t wait until it’s too late. Get unparalleled data protection. With our impenetrable encryption technology, your online data is defended against hackers, malware, and unauthorized access. Keep your data out of the reach of your adversaries. Our data protection tool works seamlessly across multiple platforms and multiple devices. Share, collaborate, and communicate with confidence. Embrace the power of unbreakable security today.
```

